node_modules/
# Analysis skills at the TOP LEVEL are personal/proprietary — bundled locally
# at build time, never committed. See skills/README.md.
# skills/builtin/ is the exception: committed, generic skills shipped with the
# repo (the negation below is a guard — `skills/*.md` does not cross the `/`).
skills/*.md
!skills/README.md
!skills/builtin/*.md
.claude/
MP Analyzer.app/
.sideloaded
dist/
.vite/
.DS_Store
*.local
~$*.xlsx
